        "description": "<p>WP Status Change Notifier allows you to notify selected users when posts&#8217; status are changed.</p>\n<p>What it does:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Notify selected users when new posts are awaiting for approval</li>\n<li>Notify contributors when posts are approved or refused</li>\n</ol>\n",
